    "body": "Closes #18210 \r\n\r\nThis PR addresses install test bugs and consistency changes from #18210 that were not subsumed by #18277.  These changes include:\r\n\r\n- Provide function for reading and converting (`re.escape`) expected output from a file\r\n- Provide consistent test part purpose/reason: `test: <verb> <description>`\r\n- Change `m4` to use the (newer) `run_test` method\r\n- Use of Spack's `join_path` (versus `os.path.join`)\r\n- Leverage (newer) ability to pass a string to `options`\r\n- Remove remaining version checks for executables that do not support the option\r\n- Fix `flake8` errors in the modified code and packages",
    "performed_via_github_app": null
